## Bottom Navigation Bar
-------------------------------------
| Recents (active) | Connections | CRM |
-------------------------------------

### Connections Tab
- Search bar (by name, handle, phone)
- Unified contact list: phone, WhatsApp, LinkedIn, etc.
- Quick actions: Message | Call | Social | Note | Reminder

### CRM Tab
- Relationship history/timeline
- Notes, tags, reminders
- Status/event sync: See client updates, business posts, etc.

### Notification Panel (Smart)
- Only from chosen contacts/groups
- Micro-interactions: like, emoji, reply
- Tap to jump into app or see post/status
